{"tid":636393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國會報告：中國不是盟友　將制定ICT供應鏈風險管理的國家戰略","createTime":"2018-04-20T20:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T20:43:17.000Z","uid":147314,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"c840362a26f880d0df30da1eba378dce3ec083b2","tid":636393,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T20:32:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://china.hket.com/article/2054608/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2054608%2F&d=rmQRCwUQjDIqh2s8OWqFumi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=b8d4a77d\" target=\"_blank\">http://china.hket.com/article/2054608/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>美國會報告點名 華為中興聯想涉間諜活動</strong><br />\n<br />\n美國國會「美中經濟與安全審查委員會」發布報告指出，中國政府可能支持某些企業進行間諜活動，以提高中企競爭力並促進政府利益；報告點名華為、中興通訊、聯想三家中企。<br />\n<br />\n「美中經濟與安全審查委員會」（US-China Economic and Security Review Commission）周四發布報告，探討中國供應鏈對美國資通訊科技（ICT）的影響。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2050000/2054608/2d779dbea904b7b56902c8e1bb4effc7_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2050000%2F2054608%2F2d779dbea904b7b56902c8e1bb4effc7_1024.jpeg&h=ecc03126&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be9e78f998fb3f2016facb8f11e8353dedf57623","tid":636393,"uid":147314,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T20:33:20.000Z","msg":"<strong>指中國一再涉及竊取與濫用知識財產權</strong><br />\n<br />\n報告明確指出，中國不是美國盟友，也不會在短時間內成為美國盟友，且中方一再涉及竊取與濫用知識財產權，以及國家主導的經濟間諜活動；中國政府政策旨在建立與支持國家龍頭企業，以進一步推動政府的戰略目標。<br />\n<br />\n報告寫道，政府的支持可採取許多種形式，但通常包括優惠貸款，在政府招標時獲優先選擇，有時還包括在受保護產業擁有壟斷地位。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，就國家龍頭企業而言，支持的方式似乎還包括官方批准或進行企業間諜活動，旨在提高中企競爭力，同時促進其它可能的政府利益；華為、中興通訊、聯想是三家具有部分上述特點的中國ICT企業。<br />\n<br />\n該報告建議，美國政府需要對ICT供應鏈風險管理的國家戰略，提倡供應鏈透明化，制定具前瞻性的政策等。"},{"pid":"61134bc52f0f302a5e0b80c5f67a5379ac4afa9f","tid":636393,"uid":147314,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T20:33:44.000Z","msg":"<strong>美商務部：中興禁令沒有協商空間 嚴格執行7年</strong><br />\n<br />\n此外，美國海軍部長史賓塞（Richard Spencer）周四在參議院軍委會聽證會也提及華為，他表示，有次要簽合約時，發現廠商的合資夥伴是華為，因此馬上停住，並表示不使用任何華為產品或軟體；史賓塞說，事態嚴重，中國不僅在南海採取行動，而是全方位。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部日前公布一項禁令，禁止美國企業未來7年內向中興通訊出售零件。中興通訊今天發布聲明稱，公司不會放棄通過溝通對話解決問題的努力，也有決心通過一切法律允許的手段維護自身的合法權益；美國商務部新聞官則表示，對於中興的禁令目前沒有扭轉的餘地或協商的空間，要嚴格地等到7年後才有望重啟協商。"},{"pid":"fafeeccc2e2072f75eead0464d5b33953b3db6d2","tid":636393,"uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T20:35:54.000Z","msg":"Supply Chain Vulnerabilities from China in U.S. Federal Information and Communications Technology<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.uscc.gov/Research/supply-chain-vulnerabilities-china-us-federal-information-and-communications-technology\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscc.gov%2FResearch%2Fsupply-chain-vulnerabilities-china-us-federal-information-and-communications-technology&d=rmQRCwUQjDIqh2s8OWqFumi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=19cf689b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.uscc.gov/Research/supply-chain-vulnerabilities-china-us-federal-information-and-communications-technology</a><br />\n<br />\nSummary: <br />\nThe U.S.-China Economic and Security Review Commission released a report entitled Supply Chain Vulnerabilities from China in U.S. Federal Information and Communications Technology, prepared for the Commission by Interos Solutions, Inc. The report examines vulnerabilities in the U.S. government information and communications technology (ICT) supply chains posed by China, and makes recommendations for supply chain risk management."},{"pid":"45e352094fdda8908545fa8ab5cd9742558292d0","tid":636393,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T20:39:11.000Z","msg":"<strong>Executive Summary</strong><br />\n<br />\nThe U.S. government needs a national strategy for supply chain risk management (SCRM) of commercial supply chain vulnerabilities in U.S. federal information and communications technology (ICT), including procurement linked to the People&rsquo;s Republic of China (China or PRC). This strategy must include supporting policies so that U.S. security posture is forward-leaning, rather than reactive and based on responding to vulnerabilities, breaches, and other incidents after they have already damaged U.S. national security, economic competitiveness, or the privacy of U.S. citizens."},{"pid":"d2b91e3bed43b21bc25e34475785671e75d9a2db","tid":636393,"uid":147314,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T20:47:41.000Z","msg":"因為真係幾長吓，有興趣自己入去繼續睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2c3b7b9d6e3aeff4ab099d8aea680ff3421c8d","tid":636393,"uid":39855,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"61134bc52f0f302a5e0b80c5f67a5379ac4afa9f","tid":636393,"uid":147314,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T20:33:44.000Z","msg":"<strong>美商務部：中興禁令沒有協商空間 嚴格執行7年</strong><br />\n<br />\n此外，美國海軍部長史賓塞（Richard Spencer）周四在參議院軍委會聽證會也提及華為，他表示，有次要簽合約時，發現廠商的合資夥伴是華為，因此馬上停住，並表示不使用任何華為產品或軟體；史賓塞說，事態嚴重，中國不僅在南海採取行動，而是全方位。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部日前公布一項禁令，禁止美國企業未來7年內向中興通訊出售零件。中興通訊今天發布聲明稱，公司不會放棄通過溝通對話解決問題的努力，也有決心通過一切法律允許的手段維護自身的合法權益；美國商務部新聞官則表示，對於中興的禁令目前沒有扭轉的餘地或協商的空間，要嚴格地等到7年後才有望重啟協商。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T20:54:10.000Z","msg":"厲害了，佢的国！"},{"pid":"fa2e94e63c325b7d3b669b0fb1570f4e606876b5","tid":636393,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T20:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ed0f890b385f166f70cd7d73890e7db3f4b78e","tid":636393,"uid":16567,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T21:01:12.000Z","msg":"支爆準備"},{"pid":"edc6aa4f1562c9b9848f1324019e101dc1594dbc","tid":636393,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T21:07:01.000Z","msg":"厲害了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42cda3fa58ac35cf6822d0bfd53b0a030ec0f7b3","tid":636393,"uid":34065,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T21:16:36.000Z","msg":"支那玩撚完<br />\n香港商人 生意佬 要飄移就快啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一陣當你支那人咁打 你就仆街了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw 嘉誠哥 真係有遠見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6d2756ef8bd4b626a37dee2381ec63d7d5145e","tid":636393,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T21:31:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong>Executive Summary</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">The U.S. government needs a national strategy for supply chain risk management (SCRM) of commercial supply chain vulnerabilities in U.S. federal information and communications technology (ICT), including procurement linked to the People&rsquo;s Republic of China (China or PRC). This strategy must include supporting policies so that U.S. security posture is forward-leaning</span>, rather than reactive and based on responding to vulnerabilities, breaches, and other incidents after they have already damaged U.S. national security, economic competitiveness, or the privacy of U.S. citizens.</blockquote><br />\n快手少少得唔得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb42252128a7b9f5b5fc05a052f70940b7da032e","tid":636393,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T21:42:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee80e7045b89d2f17119c8d9e60e088ea1de57d6","tid":636393,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T22:01:54.000Z","msg":"呢個要推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4985f7378dad74c4f6ddaf7a8e51e91f2c8c1fa","t